The paper focuses on object finding in cluttered scenes using a robotic manipulator equipped with an RGB and a depth camera. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Robotics (cs.RO) sub-category. Additionally, the paper proposes a reinforcement learning-based active and interactive perception system, which involves computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) techniques. The use of reinforcement learning also suggests that the paper may belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-category. Finally, the paper involves the use of a robotic manipulator, which suggests that it may also belong to the Systems and Control (cs.SY) sub-category.
